The,Cloud,Foundry,API,allows,developers,to,upload,and,run,applications,in,the,cloud,and,manage,them,throughout,their,lifecycles,Cloud,Foundry,is,an,open,source,multi,cloud,multi,vendor,standard,for,cloud,applications,Developers,push,their,applications,to,Cloud,Foundry,by,targeting,the,Cloud,Controller,which,stores,raw,application,bits,tracks,application,metadata,and,stages,and,runs,the,application